pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  # 顶部细线
  - elementId: top-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 1280, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 4
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: section-marker
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 20, 200, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: "CHAPTER 05 — 结论与未来工作"

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 50, 800, 35]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>5.1 研究总结与主要贡献</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 90, 1120, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#CFD8DC"

  # 三栏贡献卡片
  - elementId: card-1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 115, 350, 260]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: card-1-top
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 115, 350, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: card-1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 135, 60, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 24
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>01</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 170, 310, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>MolGNN模型框架</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-1-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 203, 310, 155]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>提出了融合边特征、GRU门控更新和注意力读出的图神经网络模型，在MoleculeNet基准上6/8个分类任务达到SOTA，平均ROC-AUC 0.842。</p>

  - elementId: card-2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [465, 115, 350, 260]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: card-2-top
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [465, 115, 350, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: card-2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [485, 135, 60, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 24
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>02</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [485, 170, 310, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>可解释性分析</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-2-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [485, 203, 310, 155]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>通过注意力权重可视化揭示了模型的决策依据，发现模型能自动识别药效团结构，与化学领域知识高度吻合，增强了模型的可信度。</p>

  - elementId: card-3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 115, 350, 260]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: card-3-top
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 115, 350, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: card-3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [870, 135, 60, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 24
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>03</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [870, 170, 310, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>系统消融研究</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-3-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [870, 203, 310, 155]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>通过系统的消融实验量化了各模块的贡献度，为分子性质预测领域的GNN模型设计提供了有价值的实证指导。</p>

  # 未来工作
  - elementId: future-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 400, 1120, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#CFD8DC"

  - elementId: future-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 420, 300, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>未来研究方向</strong></p>

  - elementId: future-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 455, 1120, 170]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      lineHeight: 1.8
      text: |
        <p><strong>方向一：</strong>引入3D分子构象信息（原子坐标、二面角），构建几何感知的GNN模型，提升构象敏感性质的预测精度。</p>
        <p><strong>方向二：</strong>探索预训练策略（分子级对比学习 + 原子级自监督），利用大规模无标注分子数据提升小样本场景的预测能力。</p>
        <p><strong>方向三：</strong>将MolGNN扩展至分子生成任务（药物设计），实现从性质预测到分子逆设计的闭环。</p>

  # 底部线
  - elementId: bottom-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 716, 1280, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 4
      color: "$primary"

  # 页码
  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1150, 680, 80, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "08 / 09"
